reviewText: Anthony Sreffen is my favourite spaghetti western actor without checking my list and seeing this cover I ordered it only to find that I had it what the hell when can you have too much of a good thing sweaty as hell lots of closeups of snarling faces more closeups of eyes and of course masses of shooting I counted eleven shots out of one gun and lost count of the many shots that were fired from many more but this is classic spaghetti great score photography its got the lot  Al Watts Radio presenter Australia
